{"tid":1425396,"cid":1,"subCid":0,"title":"零武力自衛術","createTime":"2019-08-06T18:03:20.000Z","updateTime":"2019-08-06T18:03:20.000Z","uid":29066,"like":2,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":1,"replies":[{"pid":"501020502f8fb0de272bdd8499c4351d639cbad5","tid":1425396,"uid":29066,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-06T18:03:20.000Z","msg":"最近有好多人話發噩夢比人打又或者見到其他人被打 但係有時手腳唔聽話 還唔到手 或者唔夠打<br />\n<br />\n你唯一可以做就係<span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\"><span style=\"color: red;\">大叫</span></span><br />\n大叫時要貼緊對方 然後用有震撼性嘅聲音呼救或喝止對方<br />\n<br />\n以下示範：<br />\n<a href=\"https://youtu.be/GzJeGLRat58\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fyoutu.be%2FGzJeGLRat58&d=%2FAyHQi%2FQiMXiPJLA4RPCZqha%2BoeUeRXR1jLQ0PybHu0%3D&h=5acb96b7\" target=\"_blank\">https://youtu.be/GzJeGLRat58</a><br />\n<br />\n目的除左求救之除 重最要係令對方出現耳鳴或暈眩等症狀 暫時失去攻擊能力 而且對方要告返你都咬唔入<br />\n<br />\n大叫時請注意聲量 過大聲量可引致<br />\n<span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\"><span style=\"color: red;\">聽力受損或永久性失聰</span></span><br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/hehe.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/hehe.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/hehe.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"}]}